INSERT INTO `cr_car_reviews` VALUES (1,'Really enjoyed driving this car. Plenty of legroom for everyone The car felt stable and well-balanced Impressed all our passengers Only minor complaint is the pickup location was hard to find. Highly recommend!',4,28,73,NULL,'published','2024-10-28 04:50:09','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(2,'Very pleased with this rental. Attention to detail was evident throughout Made the rental process seamless Excellent option for families Just a small issue with the owner\'s manual being missing but nothing major.',4,21,89,NULL,'published','2025-09-01 00:58:32','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(3,'Really enjoyed driving this car. Plenty of legroom for everyone Smooth acceleration and responsive braking Impressed all our passengers Only minor complaint is the car manual was missing. Highly recommend!',4,24,76,NULL,'published','2025-02-23 06:20:21','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(4,'Perfect car for our wedding! The seats were like luxury recliners The performance was absolutely flawless Exceptional attention to customer needs Cannot fault anything about this rental. 10/10 would recommend!',5,14,35,NULL,'published','2024-12-29 11:34:04','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(5,'Really enjoyed driving this car. Very quiet cabin for conversations Smooth acceleration and responsive braking Made our trip so much more enjoyable Only minor complaint is one of the USB ports wasn\'t working. Highly recommend!',4,12,60,NULL,'published','2024-09-04 13:53:12','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(6,'Absolutely fantastic! The technology was cutting-edge and intuitive Absolutely perfect reliability record Absolutely outstanding in every possible way This is how car rentals should be done. Thank you for an amazing experience!',5,26,10,NULL,'published','2025-08-31 14:59:40','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(7,'Really enjoyed driving this car. Seats were supportive and adjustable Reliable performance throughout our trip Perfect for our family vacation Only minor complaint is the return process was slightly confusing. Highly recommend!',4,29,6,NULL,'published','2024-11-16 20:51:35','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(8,'Outstanding rental experience! Surprisingly spacious for our family The car was mechanically perfect and handled like a dream on every road. They made everything so easy and stress-free Exceeded all expectations. Will definitely be back!',5,32,68,NULL,'published','2025-10-11 19:00:11','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(9,'Great rental experience! Excellent fuel economy The car was in excellent mechanical condition and performed flawlessly throughout our trip. The GPS was a bit outdated but overall very satisfied. Would definitely rent again.',4,13,88,NULL,'published','2024-06-14 23:29:28','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(10,'Very pleased with this rental. Well-maintained and cared for vehicle Quick and easy pickup process Would definitely recommend to others Just a small issue with the radio taking a moment to connect to Bluetooth but nothing major.',4,12,54,NULL,'published','2024-11-24 20:34:12','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(11,'Mixed feelings about this rental. the car was reliable throughout our trip but the customer service could be improved. Standard rental experience Fair value for money.',3,27,57,NULL,'published','2024-10-13 22:09:06','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(12,'Average rental experience. Nothing particularly stood out about this rental Minor scuff on the bumper but the pickup was convenient. Nothing special but gets the job done.',3,18,87,NULL,'published','2024-06-08 22:49:25','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(13,'Below expectations. Minor scuff on the bumper The car was reasonable considering the age but The pickup/return process. The staff was friendly enough but overall not satisfied with the rental.',2,20,32,NULL,'published','2025-10-18 00:56:04','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(14,'Very disappointed. The car showed signs of heavy use The transmission was in terrible shape and visibility was poor. Not worth the money at all.',1,31,42,NULL,'published','2025-11-14 15:02:09','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(15,'Very pleased with this rental. Well-maintained and cared for vehicle Quick and easy pickup process Great choice for anyone needing a reliable car Just a small issue with the pickup location being slightly hard to find but nothing major.',4,9,68,NULL,'published','2024-04-01 03:32:46','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(16,'Absolutely fantastic! Premium features that enhanced every moment Performed flawlessly under all conditions A truly exceptional experience from start to finish This is how car rentals should be done. Thank you for an amazing experience!',5,17,17,NULL,'published','2023-11-27 21:37:40','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(17,'Perfect car for our conference! Unparalleled comfort for long-distance driving Performance that rivals much more expensive cars Outstanding professionalism and care Cannot fault anything about this rental. 10/10 would recommend!',5,8,99,NULL,'published','2025-03-22 06:14:47','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(18,'Outstanding rental experience! Incredible fuel efficiency saved us money The car was absolutely pristine and was remarkably quiet and refined. Outstanding customer service from start to finish Exceeded all expectations. Will definitely be back!',5,31,82,NULL,'published','2025-08-21 00:51:28','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(19,'Really enjoyed driving this car. Climate control worked perfectly The engine performed well on both city and highway Handled the mountain roads beautifully Only minor complaint is the cup holders were a bit small. Highly recommend!',4,8,89,NULL,'published','2024-02-12 03:42:01','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(20,'Below expectations. The radio presets weren\'t cleared The car was reasonable considering the age but The overall value proposition. The fuel economy was good but overall not satisfied with the rental.',2,8,41,NULL,'published','2025-05-08 17:14:40','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(21,'Perfect car for our weekend getaway! Every passenger commented on the amazing comfort Outstanding handling that exceeded expectations Exceptional attention to customer needs Cannot fault anything about this rental. 10/10 would recommend!',5,20,18,NULL,'published','2025-11-16 00:56:49','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(22,'Average rental experience. Average car for an average price The pickup process took a while but the pickup was convenient. Nothing special but gets the job done.',3,24,2,NULL,'published','2025-08-21 21:19:28','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(23,'Really enjoyed driving this car. Climate control worked perfectly The engine performed well on both city and highway Perfect for our family vacation Only minor complaint is the return process was slightly confusing. Highly recommend!',4,26,59,NULL,'published','2025-02-28 14:43:34','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(24,'Horrible condition vehicle. The oil looked like it hadn\'t been changed in months I felt unsafe driving it. The turn signals were intermittent Customer service was rude when I complained.',1,17,7,NULL,'published','2024-11-29 03:58:32','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(25,'Really enjoyed driving this car. Very quiet cabin for conversations Reliable performance throughout our trip Great for city driving and parking Only minor complaint is the cup holders were a bit small. Highly recommend!',4,18,72,NULL,'published','2024-11-03 18:24:46','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(26,'Excellent value for money. Great visibility from all angles Started every time without hesitation Reliable transportation for our family trip Will book with them again for sure.',4,5,86,NULL,'published','2025-09-23 04:27:50','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(27,'Really enjoyed driving this car. Seats were supportive and adjustable Reliable performance throughout our trip Perfect for our family vacation Only minor complaint is the cup holders were a bit small. Highly recommend!',4,30,9,NULL,'published','2024-09-26 00:35:50','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(28,'Average rental experience. It was a standard rental car experience The radio presets weren\'t cleared but the staff was professional. Nothing special but gets the job done.',3,6,39,NULL,'published','2024-01-06 23:45:25','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(29,'Very pleased with this rental. Attention to detail was evident throughout Very helpful with directions Excellent option for families Just a small issue with one cup holder being a bit loose but nothing major.',4,13,8,NULL,'published','2024-05-29 01:58:22','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(30,'Decent car for the price. The interior space was adequate the pickup location being slightly hard to find but overall acceptable for conference. Would consider again if needed.',3,10,38,NULL,'published','2025-08-13 16:54:16','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(31,'Below expectations. Could use a bit more trunk space The car was acceptable but not impressive but The vehicle\'s mechanical condition. The staff was friendly enough but overall not satisfied with the rental.',2,26,19,NULL,'published','2025-03-10 07:08:14','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(32,'Horrible condition vehicle. Basic maintenance had been neglected I felt unsafe driving it. One of the headlights was dimmer than the other Customer service was rude when I complained.',1,8,92,NULL,'published','2025-05-08 11:11:34','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(33,'Average rental experience. Nothing particularly stood out about this rental Could use a bit more trunk space but the pickup was convenient. Nothing special but gets the job done.',3,9,9,NULL,'published','2024-06-18 00:45:12','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(34,'Really enjoyed driving this car. Seats were supportive and adjustable The engine performed well on both city and highway Perfect for our family vacation Only minor complaint is one of the USB ports wasn\'t working. Highly recommend!',4,12,68,NULL,'published','2025-01-24 03:38:44','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(35,'Perfect car for our family road trip! The seats were like luxury recliners Outstanding handling that exceeded expectations Service that sets the gold standard Cannot fault anything about this rental. 10/10 would recommend!',5,26,55,NULL,'published','2023-12-31 21:59:46','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(36,'Standard rental car. Served our transportation needs The pickup process took a while A typical rental car experience Met basic expectations.',3,16,4,NULL,'published','2025-01-29 08:42:23','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(37,'Best rental car I\'ve ever had! The quality was absolutely pristine Outstanding professionalism and care Worth every penny and more Everything was perfect from start to finish. Will definitely use again!',5,3,35,NULL,'published','2024-10-25 12:21:55','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(38,'Perfect car for our wedding! Exceptional ergonomics and support Exceptional driving dynamics in all conditions Outstanding professionalism and care Cannot fault anything about this rental. 10/10 would recommend!',5,1,17,NULL,'published','2024-05-26 05:17:46','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(39,'Great rental experience! Great sound system The car was in excellent mechanical condition and performed flawlessly throughout our trip. The GPS was a bit outdated but overall very satisfied. Would definitely rent again.',4,3,22,NULL,'published','2024-01-20 23:13:24','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(40,'Best rental car I\'ve ever had! The quality was absolutely pristine Staff went above and beyond at every step Best deal I\'ve found in years Everything was perfect from start to finish. Will definitely use again!',5,24,99,NULL,'published','2024-12-07 19:15:30','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(41,'Not great but manageable. The car felt underpowered on highways At least it got us where we needed to go Would look for other options next time.',2,20,87,NULL,'published','2024-10-17 05:46:08','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(42,'Average rental experience. The vehicle met basic expectations Could use a bit more trunk space but the staff was professional. Nothing special but gets the job done.',3,11,72,NULL,'published','2025-02-11 21:12:54','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(43,'Terrible experience with this car. There were scratches and dents all over The vehicle was showing significant wear and had several warning lights on. Would not recommend to anyone. Customer service was unhelpful when I reported the issues.',1,31,93,NULL,'published','2024-10-28 01:31:19','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(44,'Perfect car for our business trip! Unparalleled comfort for long-distance driving Incredible power delivery and smooth operation Exceptional attention to customer needs Cannot fault anything about this rental. 10/10 would recommend!',5,28,76,NULL,'published','2025-11-05 09:55:41','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(45,'Had some issues with this rental. The car had a persistent rattling noise interrupting our music and calls The price was reasonable but the quality didn\'t match.',2,14,80,NULL,'published','2025-07-16 10:31:42','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(46,'Absolutely fantastic! Advanced capabilities that impressed everyone Absolutely perfect reliability record This rental exceeded every expectation This is how car rentals should be done. Thank you for an amazing experience!',5,11,39,NULL,'published','2024-06-27 11:41:15','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(47,'Outstanding rental experience! Premium sound system was amazing The car was like driving a brand new car and provided effortless acceleration. The staff went above and beyond to help us Exceeded all expectations. Will definitely be back!',5,31,78,NULL,'published','2024-03-14 02:43:03','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(48,'Horrible condition vehicle. The car clearly hadn\'t been serviced recently I felt unsafe driving it. The windshield wipers were streaking badly Customer service was rude when I complained.',1,20,86,NULL,'published','2025-06-15 04:44:43','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(49,'Excellent value for money. Great visibility from all angles Completely dependable for our entire trip Reliable transportation for our family trip Will book with them again for sure.',4,4,25,NULL,'published','2024-06-08 15:23:03','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(50,'Mixed feelings about this rental. the fuel economy exceeded expectations but the vehicle felt a bit dated. Adequate for basic transportation needs Fair value for money.',3,28,90,NULL,'published','2024-09-08 09:45:37','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(51,'Really enjoyed driving this car. Incredibly comfortable for long drives Reliable performance throughout our trip Made our trip so much more enjoyable Only minor complaint is one of the USB ports wasn\'t working. Highly recommend!',4,18,55,NULL,'published','2024-04-08 15:46:36','2025-11-27 20:10:29'),(52,'Decent car for the price. The sound system worked fine the owner\'s manual being missing but overall acceptable for family road trip. Would consider again if needed.',3,1,2,NULL,'published','2025-05-29 16:04:33','2025-11-27 20:10:29');
/*!40000 ALTER TABLE `cr_car_reviews` ENABLE KEYS */;
